        vcmpgess vcmpgt_oqpd vcmpgt_oqps vcmpgt_oqsd vcmpgt_oqss vcmpgt_ospd vcmpgt_osps vcmpgt_ossd vcmpgt_osss vcmpgtpd vcmpgtps vcmpgtsd vcmpgtss vcmple_oqpd vcmple_oqps vcmple_oqsd vcmple_oqss
